# SafeHouse YouTube budget daemon — cron/nohup fallback (used when systemd is absent).
# Rendered to /etc/cron.d/safehouse-youtube-budget by ../youtube-budget/install.sh.
# The daemon is a self-looping process, so cron only needs to (re)launch it at boot;
# install.sh also nohup-starts it immediately so you don't have to reboot. Unlike the
# systemd unit there is no crash auto-restart here — check the log if enforcement stops.
# m h dom mon dow user command
@reboot root __DAEMON_SH__ >> __REPO__/logs/youtube-budget.log 2>&1
